  "detailed_description": "<h1>See also</h1><p></p><br><h1>More from XD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>From the creators of <strong>Scale Enchanter</strong>, Chords Enchanter is a <strong>music puzzle game</strong> intended for those who want to practice chord building in a <i>relaxing</i> and <i>completely imersive</i> environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1655460136\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chord Building</h2>Made for any <strong>music student</strong> or <strong>master</strong> that wants to practice chord building.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/99ea3f33371ae2af1e6d6f1cf342764e.poster.avif?t=1655460136\" width=678 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/99ea3f33371ae2af1e6d6f1cf342764e.webm?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/99ea3f33371ae2af1e6d6f1cf342764e.mp4?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >140+ Chords</h2><strong>Over 140 chords</strong> to build from 10 differente chord types.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Imersive Environment</h2>Feel like in a <strong>concert</strong>, in an environment full of <strong>music elements</strong>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/9e4829476db0d7073ff3ec726d30423c.poster.avif?t=1655460136\" width=800 height=606 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/9e4829476db0d7073ff3ec726d30423c.webm?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/9e4829476db0d7073ff3ec726d30423c.mp4?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relaxing and joyful</h2><strong>Take your time</strong> to build the chords, and if you want to go back to an already built chord, it's <i>just like that</i>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd3a94d9c82dbe2d564c6d69bd91d442.poster.avif?t=1655460136\" width=800 height=606 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd3a94d9c82dbe2d564c6d69bd91d442.webm?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977360/extras/dd3a94d9c82dbe2d564c6d69bd91d442.mp4?t=1655460136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Let's practice together? <strong>Wishlist now</strong> to keep in touch with the release date!",
